    public class EnumSetConverter<CONTEXT,E extends Enum<E>>
extends LongConverterBase<CONTEXT,EnumSet<E>>
implements ConfiguredConverter<CONTEXT,EnumSet<E>>
    EnumSetConverter implements a LongConverter for some enum type. It is assumed that there are no more then 64 values for this enum.
